---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
	title="Corporate Catering Vancouver | Office Lunch & Conference Catering | Sula"
	description="Premium corporate Indian catering in Vancouver since 2010. Boardroom lunches, office catering, conference meals. Halal, vegetarian, vegan. Reliable Lower Mainland delivery."
	canonical="/corporate"
	ogImage="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/indian-catering-vancouver-burnaby-richmond-for-corporate-offices-private-parties-and-weddings.webp"
>

	<Fragment slot="schema">
		<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
			"@context": "https://schema.org",
			"@type": "Service",
			"name": "Corporate Indian Catering Vancouver",
			"provider": { "@id": "https://sulacatering.com/#organization" },
			"areaServed": ["Vancouver", "Burnaby", "Richmond", "Surrey", "North Vancouver"],
			"serviceType": "Corporate Catering",
			"description": "Office and corporate Indian catering in Vancouver — boardroom lunches, conferences, team celebrations with reliable hot delivery."
		})} />
	</Fragment>

	<section class="hero" style="background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(20,8,16,0.85) 0%, rgba(38,14,38,0.7) 50%, rgba(20,8,16,0.9) 100%), url('https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/indian-catering-vancouver-burnaby-richmond-for-corporate-offices-private-parties-and-weddings.webp');">
		<div class="hero-content">
			<p class="gold-label">Office & Corporate Catering</p>
			<h1>Corporate Indian Catering<br/>in <em>Vancouver</em></h1>
			<p class="hero-tagline">Reliable office catering for boardroom lunches, all-day conferences, and team celebrations — delivered hot, on time, every time.</p>
			<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-gold">Request a Quote</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="intro-block reveal">
				<p class="gold-label">Trusted by Vancouver's Top Companies</p>
				<h2>Office Lunches, <em>Done Right</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament">
					<span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span>
				</div>
				<p>Sula caters daily office lunches and corporate events across downtown Vancouver, Burnaby, Richmond, and Surrey. Hot delivery, professional presentation, and zero-delay execution — because your team's lunch hour matters, and your guests' first impression matters more.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/office-catering-vancouver-bc.webp" alt="Office catering Vancouver BC" class="full-width-image" loading="lazy" />

	<section class="section section-dark">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="alt-row">
				<div class="alt-row-img reveal-left">
					<img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Indian-food-catering-vancouver-bc-canada.webp" alt="Boardroom lunch catering Vancouver" loading="lazy" />
				</div>
				<div class="alt-row-content reveal-right">
					<p class="gold-label">Boardroom Lunches</p>
					<h2>Quiet Precision, <em>Powerful Flavours</em></h2>
					<p>Individually packed thalis or buffet trays for client meetings and executive lunches. We arrive on time, set up quietly, and disappear — leaving your team to focus on what matters.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="alt-row reverse">
				<div class="alt-row-img reveal-right">
					<img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Indian-food-catering-vancouver-burnaby-richmond.webp" alt="Conference catering Vancouver" loading="lazy" />
				</div>
				<div class="alt-row-content reveal-left">
					<p class="gold-label">All-Day Conferences</p>
					<h2>Breakfast to <em>Tea Break</em></h2>
					<p>Full-day conference catering — breakfast pastries, mid-morning chai service, hot lunch buffets, and afternoon tea. Add a chai station from Sula Café to keep energy high through the final session.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="alt-row">
				<div class="alt-row-img reveal-left">
					<img src="https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/indian-catering-near-me-vancouver-birthdays-parties.webp" alt="Team celebration catering Vancouver" loading="lazy" />
				</div>
				<div class="alt-row-content reveal-right">
					<p class="gold-label">Team Celebrations</p>
					<h2>Holiday Parties, <em>Milestones, Wins</em></h2>
					<p>Birthdays, holiday parties, project wins — full Indian feasts brought directly to your office. Buffet style, family style, or plated. We adapt to your space and your team.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<div class="image-banner" style="background-image: url('https://backend.sulaindianrestaurant.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/indian-catering-near-me-vancouver.webp');">
		<div class="image-banner-content reveal">
			<h2>Recurring Catering, <em>Effortless Setup</em></h2>
			<p>Weekly or monthly meal plans for offices that take care of their teams.</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="gold-label">Service Styles</p>
				<h2 style="font-size:42px;font-weight:400">Buffet, Plated, or <em style="color:var(--gold)">Drop-Off</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament">
					<span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="services-grid">
				<div class="service-card reveal">
					<h3>Drop-Off</h3>
					<p>Hot trays delivered to your office. Simple, fast, and perfect for quick team lunches.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="service-card reveal delay-100">
					<h3>Buffet Service</h3>
					<p>Full setup with chafing dishes, serving utensils, and labels. Casual yet professional.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="service-card reveal delay-200">
					<h3>Plated Lunch</h3>
					<p>Individually plated meals for executive lunches and formal corporate events.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="service-card reveal delay-300">
					<h3>Recurring Plans</h3>
					<p>Weekly or monthly catering with rotating menus, dietary tracking, and priority scheduling.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-dark">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="testimonial-block reveal">
				<p class="gold-label">From Our Clients</p>
				<p class="testimonial-quote">We've been ordering from Sula every month for two years. They never miss. The food shows up hot, the team loves it, and the whole process is effortless.</p>
				<p class="testimonial-author">— Office Manager · Downtown Vancouver Tech Firm</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="gold-label">Common Questions</p>
				<h2 style="font-size:42px;font-weight:400">Corporate Catering <em style="color:var(--gold)">FAQs</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament">
					<span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="faq-list">
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>What is the minimum order for office catering?</h3><p>Our minimum is typically 10 guests. For smaller orders, takeout from any Sula location works great.</p></div>
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>Can you accommodate dietary restrictions?</h3><p>Yes — we offer vegetarian, vegan, halal, gluten-friendly, and dairy-free options on every menu. Just let us know your team's needs.</p></div>
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>How much notice do you need?</h3><p>48 hours minimum for most corporate orders. Larger events (50+ guests) benefit from a week's notice. We do our best with rush requests.</p></div>
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>Do you deliver across the Lower Mainland?</h3><p>Yes — Vancouver, Burnaby, Richmond, Surrey, North Vancouver, and West Vancouver. Delivery fees vary by distance.</p></div>
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>Can we set up a recurring catering plan?</h3><p>Absolutely. Many of our clients order weekly or monthly with rotating menus tailored to their team.</p></div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="cta-section">
		<div class="reveal">
			<p class="gold-label" style="color:var(--gold-light)">Begin the Conversation</p>
			<h2>Feed Your Team <em>Beautifully</em></h2>
			<p>Tell us about your event. We'll respond within 24 hours with a custom menu and quote.</p>
			<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-gold">Request a Quote</a>
		</div>
	</section>

</Layout>
